Class AbstractConfigurationFactory<T extends Configuration>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.codeleaf.config.impl.AbstractConfigurationFactory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the configuration that is supported
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuthenticationConfigurationFactory, BasicConfigurationFactory, DummyConfigurationFactory, ElasticLogConfigurationFactory

    public abstract class AbstractConfigurationFactory<T extends Configuration>
extends Object
implements ConfigurationFactory
    This class represents a configuration factory that creates only a single type.

    0.1.0
